               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael (fols.
                     2ra-104vb) 
 I-1) Homily by Timothy (Damātewos), Patriarch of Alexandria
                     for the 12th of Ḫǝdār (fols. 2ra-7vb); miracle (fols. 8ra-10rb); commemorative
                     notice (fols. 10rb-11vb); ʾarke-hymn (fols. 11vb-12rb) 
 I-2) Homily by an
                     anonymous author for Tāḫśāś (fols. 12rb-17vb); miracle (fols. 17vb-19rb);
                     commemorative notice (fols. 19rb-20ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 20ra-rb) 
 I-3)
                     Homily [by Epiphanius, Metropolitan of Cyprus] for Ṭǝrr (fols. 20ra-29ra);
                     miracle (fol. 29ra-vb); commemorative notice (fol. 30ra-vb); ʾarke-hymn (fol.
                     30vb) 
 I-4) Homily by an anonymous author for Yakkātit (fols. 31ra-34ra);
                     miracle (fols. 34ra-35ra); commemorative notice (fol. 35ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol.
                     35ra-rb) 
 I-5) Homily by [Severus] Patriarch of Antiochia for the 12th of
                     Maggābit (fols. 35va-51ra); miracle (fols. 51rb-52rb); commemorative notice
                     (fol. 52rb-va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 52va-vb) 
 I-6) Homily by [Metropolitan
                     Yoḥannǝs] the Orthodox for Miyāzyā (fols. 53ra-57rb); miracle (fols. 57rb
                     -58va); commemorative notice (fol. 58va-vb); ʾarke-hymn (fols. 58vb-59rb) 
                     I-7) Homily by Patriarch Yoḥannǝs ʾAfa Warq [Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of
                     Ethiopia] for the 12th of Gǝnbot (fols. 59va-65ra); miracle (fols. 65ra-66vb);
                     commemorative notice (fols. 66vb-67rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 67rb) 
 I-8)
                     Homily by Yoḥannǝs, ʾeṗisqoṗos [Metropolitan] of ʾAksum for Sane (fols.
                     68ra-73vb); miracle (fols. 73vb-75ra); commemorative notice (fols. 75ra-81vb);
                     ʾarke-hymn (fols. 81vb-82rb) 
 I-9) Homily [by Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs] for
                     Ḥamle (fols. 82va-86vb); miracle (fol. 87ra-vb); commemorative notice (fols.
                     87vb-88rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 88rb-vb) 
 I-10) Homily by an anonymous author
                     for Naḥāse (fols. 89ra-92ra); miracle (fol. 92ra-va); commemorative notice
                     (fols. 92vb-93ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 93ra-rb) 
 I-11) Homily by an anonymous
                     author for Maskaram (fols. 93va-96ra); miracle (fol. 96rb-vb); commemorative
                     notice (fols. 96vb-97rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 97rb) 
 I-12) Homily by an
                     anonymous author for Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 97va-101vb); miracle (fols. 101vb-104ra);
                     commemorative notice (fol. 104ra-vb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 104vb) 
 
                     Additiones 1-4.</summary>
