                                 59va</locus> ዘሰኔ: <locus target="#68ra">fol. 68ra</locus>
                              ዘሃ[sic]ምሌ: <locus target="#82va">fol. 82va</locus> ዘነሃ[sic]ሴ፡ ነው:
